@{b}@{u}Registered version@{ub}@{uu}

Registered version of this software includes all files, as this
distribution, plus personalized "keyfile", which will disable all the
irritating reminders.

Distribution of the registered version is handled via mail. You will receive
your copy in one DD-disk.


